{
  "id": "69c2ee0a03e62e8de6b77fa8",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:ここを見ればなんでも書いてある場所",
  "created": 1774382628,
  "updated": 1774382645,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c2ee0a03e62e8de6b77fa8",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:ここを見ればなんでも書いてある場所",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382628,
      "updated": 1774382628
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee240000000000d6a124",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382628,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a125",
      "text": "「はいはーい、今日のテーマは〜『[ここを見ればなんでも書いてある場所]』でーす！いわゆる最強の攻略wiki的なやつね。これ一個で全部わかる、みたいな。神サイト降臨って感じで草」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a126",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a127",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a128",
      "text": "「まあ……なんと心強い響きでしょう。迷い子が道しるべを得るような……そんな場所ですのね（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a129",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a12a",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a12b",
      "text": "「定義を先に置く。『なんでも書いてある』は、網羅性・正確性・更新性の三要素で構成される。どれか欠けると“なんでも”は成立しない」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a12c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a12d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a12e",
      "text": "「出た、りかの三点セット！でもわかる。更新止まってるwikiとか、普通に罠だしね。“最終更新：2013年”とか見た瞬間にHP削られる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a12f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a130",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a131",
      "text": "「時の流れに取り残された知識は、ときに誤解を招きますものね。けれど、その古さにもまた趣が……いえ、実用という点では難しいかもしれませんわ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a132",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a133",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a134",
      "text": "「趣は別カテゴリ。実用性とは分離すべき。例えばWikipediaは一定の信頼性があるが、専門領域では一次情報に当たる必要がある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a135",
      "text": "https://ja.wikipedia.org/",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a136",
      "text": "ただし、出典の有無を確認するのが前提」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a137",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a138",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a139",
      "text": "「うわ、出典チェック勢だ。ガチじゃん。でもさ、“なんでも書いてある場所”って、ぶっちゃけGoogle先生じゃね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a13a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a13b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a13c",
      "text": "「検索エンジンは“入口”。場所ではない。情報のインデックスだ。だから最終的な“場所”は個々のサイトに分散する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a13d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a13e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a13f",
      "text": "「なるほど……入口と居場所は異なるのですね。まるで図書館の目録と書架の関係のようでございますね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a140",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a141",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a142",
      "text": "「あや、それ例えエモい。つまり“最強の場所”って、実在するというより“いろんな場所の集合体”ってこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a143",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a144",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a145",
      "text": "「その解釈が最も現実的。分散知識ベース。単一の完全体は存在しない。近いものとしてはStack OverflowのようなQ&Aサイト",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a146",
      "text": "https://stackoverflow.com/",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a147",
      "text": "ただし分野限定」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a148",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a149",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a14a",
      "text": "「プログラミング限定じゃん！ゲームの裏技とか恋愛相談とかは無理ゲー」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a14b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a14c",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a14d",
      "text": "「恋の悩みまで網羅する場所……それはもはや神託の領域ではありませんこと？（笑う）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a14e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a14f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a150",
      "text": "「神託APIは現在未実装。リクエストは受理されていない」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a151",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a152",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a153",
      "text": "「何それ実装してｗ でもさ、TikTokとかSNSも“なんでも載ってる感”あるよね。玉石混交だけど」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a154",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a155",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a156",
      "text": "「情報の信頼性が低い。アルゴリズムによる最適化で偏る。エコーチェンバー問題が発生する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a157",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a158",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a159",
      "text": "「偏った風だけを受け続けると、やがて世界の広さを忘れてしまいそうで……少し怖いですわね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a15a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a15b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a15c",
      "text": "「あー、それな。好きなやつばっか流れてくるの、楽だけど危険でもあるやつ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a15d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a15e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a15f",
      "text": "「要点を整理する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a160",
      "text": " 1. 完全な“なんでも書いてある場所”は現実には存在しない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a161",
      "text": " 2. 近似は複数の信頼できるソースの組み合わせ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a162",
      "text": " 3. 利用者のリテラシーが品質を決定する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a163",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a164",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a165",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a166",
      "text": "「はい出ました、まとめ助かる〜！結局“自分で見極めろ”ってやつね。ラスボスじゃん」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a167",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a168",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a169",
      "text": "「けれど、それもまた学びの一部なのかもしれませんわね。知を探す旅路そのものが、私たちを豊かにしてくれるのですから（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a16a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a16b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a16c",
      "text": "「詩的だが、概ね同意。最適解は“複数参照＋検証”。それが現代の知識探索プロトコル」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a16d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a16e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a16f",
      "text": "「結論：最強の場所は“自分の頭＋ネットの合わせ技”ってことか〜。なんかRPGでいうパーティ編成みたいでアツい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a170",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a171",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a172",
      "text": "「それぞれの強みを活かして、ひとつの答えに辿り着く……美しい協調でございますね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a173",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a174",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a175",
      "text": "「では、この鼎談自体も小さな“知識ノード”として記録されるべきだ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a176",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a177",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a178",
      "text": "「急に中二発動ｗ でもいいね、それ。“ここ見ればちょっと役立つ”くらいにはなったっしょ！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a179",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a17a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2ee250000000000d6a17b",
      "text": "「ええ、ささやかな灯火でも、誰かの道を照らせますように（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774382629,
      "updated": 1774382629
